Package org.wsmo.grounding.sawsdl

Interface Summary
AttributeModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from an XML Schema attribute definition to a concept of a semantic model.
ComplexTypeModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from an XML Schema complexType definition to a concept of a semantic model.
ElementModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from an XML Schema element definition to a concept of a semantic model.
FaultModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from a WSDL 2.0 operation fault definition to a concept of a semantic model.
For details see:
http://www.w3.org/TR/sawsdl/
http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl20/
Grounding A grounding object containing all SAWSDL annotations of a single WSDL document.
InterfaceCategory Representation of a single annotation reference from a WSDL 2.0 interface definition to a concept of a semantic model.
For details see:
http://www.w3.org/TR/sawsdl/
http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl20/
LiftingSchemaMapping A lifting schema mapping for a certain XML Schema element.
For details see:
http://www.w3.org/TR/sawsdl/
http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema/
LoweringSchemaMapping A lowering schema mapping for a certain XML Schema element.
For details see:
http://www.w3.org/TR/sawsdl/
http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema/
ModelRef An abstract representation of a semantic model annotation of a WSDL or XML Schema entity.
OperationModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from a WSDL 2.0 operation definition to a concept of a semantic model.
For details see:
http://www.w3.org/TR/sawsdl/
http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl20/
SchemaMapping An abstract schema mapping for a certain XML Schema element.
SimpleTypeModelRef Representation of a single annotation reference from an XML Schema simpleType definition to a concept of a semantic model.
TypeModelRef Abstract representation of a single annotation reference from an XML Schema type (simple or complex) definition to a concept of a semantic model.
